				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/153/sirena-a-song-the-black-mermaid-might-sing">Sirena: a song the black mermaid might sing</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/margaret-mackinnon">Margaret MacKinnon</a></li><li><a href="/issues/153">August 1988</a></li></ul>

		

